Maintainer: Harpreet Kaur <harpreet.kaur2@nih.gov>, <hks04180@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a pipeline for predicting the survival probability of cancer patients. It includes data processing, data normalization, feature selection, LASSO PI Score generation, development of prediction models, and visualization tools.
